MONTH 6 — Deployment + Evaluation (June 2026)
-----------------------------------------------
Week 19 — Deployment

- Deploy frontend to Vercel
- Deploy API to Render or Fly.io
- Set all environment variables in production
- Point n8n to production API URL
- Full end-to-end test in production

Week 20 — System Testing + ISO Evaluation Prep

Thesis requires evaluation based on ISO/IEC 25010:2018:
- Functional Suitability  → use-case testing checklist
- Performance Efficiency  → measure API response times
- Compatibility           → test on Chrome, Firefox, Edge, mobile
- Usability               → survey with admin and staff
- Reliability             → uptime, error handling
- Security                → auth routes, SQL injection tests
- Maintainability         → code documentation
- Portability             → responsive on laptop + mobile

Prepare UAT survey forms for BellahBeatrix staff.
Conduct actual UAT at the General Trias, Cavite office.

Week 21 — Demo Prep + Thesis Finalization

