RISK MANAGEMENT
---------------
Facebook App Review slow    → Apply today, use mock post in demo if needed
Forecast model complex      → Use moving average first, upgrade later
n8n breaks in production    → Keep manual Post Now button on every post
Auth breaks existing flow   → Keep mock AuthContext working until Supabase Auth confirmed
Running out of time         → Cut Trending Keywords + Activity Log last
ISO evaluation forms late   → Draft survey forms now, don't wait until Month 6


